Come on, Yukinari.

14
00:02:52,250 --> 00:02:54,291
Let's take a nice
hot bath together.

15
00:02:54,375 --> 00:02:57,250
Stop! I told you,
if I don't hurry up,

16
00:02:57,333 --> 00:02:59,791
I'm not going to make
it to class on time!

17
00:02:59,875 --> 00:03:03,041
Taking a bath is more
important than going to school.

18
00:03:03,125 --> 00:03:04,250
Wah!

19
00:03:04,333 --> 00:03:05,583
Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow!

20
00:03:05,666 --> 00:03:07,250
--[MIHARU] Hurry up already.
--[KIRIE growling]

21
00:03:07,333 --> 00:03:09,208
[YUKINARI]
N-no no no! You can't!

22
00:03:09,291 --> 00:03:11,375
Not my underwear!
Not my underwear!

23
00:03:11,458 --> 00:03:13,958
You can't wear them
into the bathtub, silly.

24
00:03:14,041 --> 00:03:15,583
Uh, Kirie?

25
00:03:15,666 --> 00:03:17,125
Good morning, there.

26
00:03:17,208 --> 00:03:19,083
Oh, do you wanna
take a bath, too?

27
00:03:19,166 --> 00:03:21,375
No, Kirie, w-w-w-w-wait.
This isn't what you think!

28
00:03:21,458 --> 00:03:23,166
It's not like that!

29
00:03:23,250 --> 00:03:25,291
--[YUKINARI] It's not--
--[MIHARU beating up YUKINARI]

30
00:03:31,083 --> 00:03:32,166
[KIRIE]
Sorry.

31
00:03:32,250 --> 00:03:33,791
[YUKINARI] I think it
stinks how you always

32
