that much?

65
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:55,375
Yeah. I like that
curry rice from yesterday, too.

66
00:04:55,458 --> 00:04:59,291
But I think the bread I ate
right now is even better.

67
00:04:59,375 --> 00:05:02,416
Okay then.
Hey, I know!

68
00:05:02,500 --> 00:05:04,166
I'll bring back
some bread for you

69
00:05:04,250 --> 00:05:06,500
