from school today.

70
00:05:06,583 --> 00:05:08,458
From school?

71
00:05:08,541 --> 00:05:10,250
So you can buy
bread where you learn?

72
00:05:10,333 --> 00:05:13,791
Uh-huh! The school bread almost
makes it worth having to go.

73
00:05:13,875 --> 00:05:15,791
The school bread...

74
00:05:15,875 --> 00:05:17,208
There are a lot
of different types,

75
00:05:17,291 --> 00:05:19,541
but the best is the bread
with the curry inside.

76
00:05:19,625 --> 00:05:20,541
[MIHARU gasps]

77
00:05:20,625 --> 00:05:22,291
It's curry bread!

78
00:05:22,375 --> 00:05:24,875
Oh yeah. It's so
popular it sells out

79
00:05:24,958 --> 00:05:26,250
as soon as the
lunch bell rings.

80
00:05:26,333 --> 00:05:28,333
I would just
love to try some.

81
00:05:28,416 --> 00:05:30,458
Okay, then I guess
I'll get you some.

82
00:05:30,541 --> 00:05:32,708
Thank you, I am
kind of hungry again.

83
00:05:32,791 --> 00:05:34,541
Oh.

84
00:05:34,625 --> 00:05:42,125
