[GIRL 1] Oh, Fukuyama,
you shouldn't touch me there.

188
00:11:42,500 --> 00:11:44,416
You're such a naughty boy.

189
00:11:44,500 --> 00:11:46,333
[GIRL 2] Oh, Fukuyama, save some
for me.

190
00:11:46,416 --> 00:11:47,458
