200
00:12:05,708 --> 00:12:07,208
All you do is sit
in the back of the class

201
00:12:07,291 --> 00:12:09,250
and act like King Pervert!

202
00:12:09,333 --> 00:12:12,458
News flash, pal,
you're seventeen!

203
00:12:12,541 --> 00:12:15,500
And why are you the only
one wearing a white uniform?

204
00:12:15,583 --> 00:12:17,291
You are so damn pretentious!

205
00:12:17,375 --> 00:12:20,833
Why, Kirie,
I'm surprised at you.

206
00:12:20,916 --> 00:12:22,833
If you wanted to
be part of the group,

207
00:12:22,916 --> 00:12:25,708
all you had to do was ask.

208
00:12:25,791 --> 00:12:26,875
[GYM INSTRUCTOR]
Mizuno High School! Fight!

209
00:12:26,958 --> 00:12:28,250
[INSTURCTOR]
