210
00:12:28,333 --> 00:12:30,916
[STUDENTS] Uh! Uh! Uh! Uh!

211
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:31,916
Kirie again?

212
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:33,125
Yeah, Fukuyama I bet.

213
00:12:33,208 --> 00:12:35,125
What is that,
the 27th window this month?

214
00:12:35,208 --> 00:12:37,291
They don't let up, do they?

215
00:12:37,375 --> 00:12:38,958
[FUKUYAMA giggles]

216
00:12:39,041 --> 00:12:41,500
Kirie, you really
should do something

217
00:12:41,583 --> 00:12:43,166
