horrible temper.

218
00:12:43,250 --> 00:12:45,333
You'll never catch
a husband that way.

219
00:12:45,416 --> 00:12:48,166
Like I need
your advice on love!

220
00:12:48,250 --> 00:12:49,375
Yukinari, go ahead!

221
00:12:49,458 --> 00:12:50,791
Huh?

222
00:12:50,875 --> 00:12:54,000
Come on! Put this white
uniform pervert in his place!

223
00:12:54,083 --> 00:12:56,041
No, I'll pass.

224
00:12:56,125 --> 00:12:58,333
[FUKUYAMA laughs maniacally]

225
00:12:58,416 --> 00:13:00,500
Now that's just cruel, Kirie!

226
00:13:00,583 --> 00:13:04,333
My family is super rich!
I'm practically 6 feet tall!

227
00:13:04,416 --> 00:13:06,625
Of all the guys at
Mizuno High School,

228
00:13:06,708 --> 00:13:08,625
