229
00:13:08,708 --> 00:13:12,000
[FUKUYAMA giggles maniacally]

230
00:13:12,083 --> 00:13:14,541
How could poor little
Puny-nari Sasaki,

231
00:13:14,625 --> 00:13:17,916
the class runt,
possibly put me in my place?!

232
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:20,416
[FUKUYAMA laughs maniacally]

233
00:13:20,500 --> 00:13:21,583
Dumbass.

234
00:13:21,666 --> 00:13:23,750
Just who the hell
do you think you are?

235
00:13:23,833 --> 00:13:27,000
I know Yukinari, and there are
lots of great things about him.

236
00:13:27,083 --> 00:13:30,083
--[YUKINARI] Kirie?
--[KIRIE] He's nice.

237
00:13:30,166 --> 00:13:32,625
--What's up with Kirie?
--And he's funny.

238
00:13:32,708 --> 00:13:34,541
And he's way more mature
than someone like you

239
00:13:34,625 --> 00:13:36,583
who goes around all day
with his brain in his pants!

240
00:13:36,666 --> 00:13:39,500
And one more thing,
I know about you...

241
00:13:39,583 --> 00:13:41,375
The chink in your armor...

242
00:13:41,458 --> 00:13:45,416
The secret behind
these white gloves.

243
00:13:45,500 --> 00:13:49,416
Ha! Guess I'll
enjoy the view!

244
00:13:49,500 --> 00:13:51,416
[KIRIE gasps]

245
00:13:51,500 --> 00:13:54,208
I'll make you mine,
one way or another, Kirie!

246
00:13:54,291 --> 00:13:56,125
I think my secret's
safe with you.

247
00:13:56,208 --> 00:14:00,000
The right one, the left?
Which one's enjoying it more?

248
00:14:00,083 --> 00:14:01,416
[FUKUYAMA making kissing sound]

249
00:14:01,500 --> 00:14:03,041
